Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，我也很想去那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊，在那之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…借點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與學園關係匪淺的各大企業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和本校畢業生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及本地企業的協助之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:01:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今年也能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8話最重視的事物。\N盛大地迎接創立祭來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請各位充分享受祭典吧\N阿和，我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命，妳想去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊!我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這撒嬌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣不在還是會覺得寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多36度8吧\N幾乎已經是正常體溫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就說我沒事了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命學姐不是在等妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有拜託千繪她們照顧她了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了一點汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳，別這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做無謂的抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安分點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的小賊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我幫你換…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為有色女潛入了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們姊弟絕～對有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒也退了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一會兒就可以\N去執行實行委員的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你操心\N就好好跟姊姊撒嬌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這戀姊癖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價錢挺公道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是拉麵店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來!日珥一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子不夠？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，我去想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了，楯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那組還真悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是事前準備程度的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本來\N想跟哥哥一起逛的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是笨蛋!笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜，等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊，就去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係，兩個人一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去…看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的旅行也還沒決定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和你死相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在想色色的事情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有好～多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟阿和一起逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主如是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如芥菜種子一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個種子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學，畢竟機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也去逛一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父那邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來跟他說明就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著讓我來幫忙吧，紫子修女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石上老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事情\N請問妳有沒有考慮過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很困擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要我當畫作的模特兒\N我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊\N雖然有聽說這間學校很有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還真的是很不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像來錯地方一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得，妳比平常更有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我決定\N今天要好好享受一番啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，接著想去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是託舞衣的福，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟妳道謝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，還讓你幫忙我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館地下室\N應該還有幾張備用桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城建設公司推出驚悚鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠承受這份恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子還不夠力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，妳好過份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是\N很不習慣這種氣氛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於明年度\N貴校採用敝社產品一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是用茶的時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傷感情的話題等會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，可是我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長已經全權委任於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚點我會好好聽你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微在人前露個臉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應付那些老小孩的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是交給藤乃同學也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你請暫時歇息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白小姐，請別讓二三難做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，還讓妳來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，反正只是順便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳力氣太多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛網啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!蜘蛛？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳背上有蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開…開玩笑的，開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，是我不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你道歉沒有誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 妳!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然越難搞的女生越可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳也\N差不多該下定決心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，方便的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳能離開一下\N我會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海～!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊～!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎學長～!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也不通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命～!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，那隻狂飆小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了吧妳!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧也鬧夠了，吃也吃夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這傢伙的主人說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫她好好教導一下這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後給她綁個項圈\N或者關進籠子裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，接著就是各位引頸企盼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本校得以自誇的黃金天使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成員含有小學部的\N艾莉莎．西爾斯的聖歌隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在決定交往的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說好不要對彼此有所隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得要告訴你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學校地下…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間學校到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，越來越讓人不爽!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會碰到這種事\N全～都是那個笨蛋楯害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是巧海出了什麼意外\N我絕對不會放過他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他也只是\N想開個小玩笑而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以問妳一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是喜歡楯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥～？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然冒出這種話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙，當然是完全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想甩他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我跟詩帆約好了…\N那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以考慮考慮我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該消遣那個粗心大魔王的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊從以前真的就只怕蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然只是\N一個普通的高中女生，是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也問過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會搶走妳的姊姊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜同學，請救救我!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的怪物又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（那些寂寞的少女們）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（被囚禁在月亮背面的\N荊棘之城，是誰？）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這12名少女\N閃耀著虛無飄渺的光芒）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（有如幾千年\N才綻放一次的花朵一般）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那場公車意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被深優同學看到以來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（只是夢想著\N她們能夠自由飛翔的場所）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會被阿和知道…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總會想，為什麼是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對我說這是世界的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有什麼很深刻的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可怕～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要接納你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該是為了\N要守護我最重視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎…學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長!為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊…姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很噁心對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能會因為這麼一點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，深優同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳並沒有\N把妳看到的事情說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該要道謝的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳讓我收集到很珍貴的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我再試驗一樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（複合式人格世界樹裝置）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N舞衣也走上我安排的路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開…眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時候說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要賭上妳最重視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並非指妳的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳最重視的人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是通到這裡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創立祭已經結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下後夜祭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本要在渡輪上舉行\N然後去事前調查…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳牽扯上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種幾條命都不夠賠的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要賭上妳最重視的事物…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」\N這句話我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life\N總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼\N現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海與少女與夏姬的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海與少女與夏姬的秘密\N問一下喔\N女孩子最重要的東西是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是很容易\N在夏天的海邊失去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…對了，錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易遺失啊，畢竟穿泳衣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔!我還以為是×××呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿和呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟阿和開始交往時的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然把你找來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.75,0:24:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去雖然沒有跟你同班過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.19,0:24:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很注意和也同學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然聽到這種話\N任誰都會呆住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N我想至少要告訴你我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.33,0:24:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.60,0:24:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你聽我說!掰掰!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.34,0:24:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.85,0:24:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…像我這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.85,0:24:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不，不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.99,0:24:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.39,0:25:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的創立祭上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.46,0:25:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告訴阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.30,0:25:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直說不出口的事情…


